level.text: 3400.1 This chapter shall apply to applicants for and holders of a license toractice architecture.
3400.2 Chapter 33 of this Title shall supplement this chapter.
3400.3 The provisions of this chapter and the Act shall prevail in the event of direct and irreconcilable conflict between this chapter or the Act and Chapter3 of this Title.
